<br>
She kept her mouth shut and spoke to them telepathically, she, not having a voice of her own, spoke with the soft voice of a young mortal she had heard sing the other day.<br>
<br>
~Welcome friends, this is Hera's surprise baby shower. Seeing that no one but she knew about the child before it's birth, we are giving her one now.~<br>
<br>
She smiled seeing Hippolyte of Themiscrya, Hipp's presence would sure bring a smile to Hera's face.<br>
<br>
~We will be having blessings upon the child, gifts, feasting and drinking, and perhaps even a few games.~<br>
<br>
She smiled to Mojo, Sartha, Shey, Dawn and the others.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Megaera appeared along with Alecto near the center of the room. Meg instantly grabbed a small chalice and filled it with wine.<br>
<br>
Alecto placed her hands on her hips looking at the turnout.<br>
&quot;So where are all the guys?&quot; She grinned.<br>
<br>
Tisiphone sighed seeing her sisters, as much as she loved them, Alecto was a pain every now and then. But it was after all in her nature to be one. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Nike Goddess of Victory</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#FFFF33>(6/12/01 9:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=70.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Baby Shower</span><hr size=1> ::a golden rainbow glitters in the room, Nike appears standing in it , the rainbow fades away. Is donning a fresh white silk toga with a light pink robe wrapping around her body with a thin golden ribbon to hold it on. Her hair is up with golden string woven through it and a thin golden necklace. Is carrying a cage covered by a violet silk cloth and is breathing hard:: <br>
