<br>
::He begins padding himself and feeling in the pockets and pouches of the robe.  He then puts his finger straight into the air as if to remember where it was::<br>
<br>
&quot;Ah yes...&quot;<br>
<br>
::He walks over to a shadow and reaches into it.  His hand seems to disappear into it until he finally pulls out a small wooden rocking horse...which looks remarkably like a minature version of the infamous Trojan horse.  He smirked and set the rocking horse down on the floor and continued walking about the room:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=sartha>Sartha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 92<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(6/14/01 3:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=70.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SECRET FEAST OF THE GODS, ALL ARE INVITED!!!</span><hr size=1> ::figures she might as well change and glides a hand over her leathers, replacing them with a long golden dress that hung over matching shoes. It had no sleeves and a few straps, most cascading down her arms, two upholding the dress on either side. She hair, instead of down, is thrown into a neat bun wraped with a string of golden ribbon. Walks to Shey and smiles lightly::<br>
